{"type":null,"faqId":49623,"title":"荣耀小K运动计步数据没有或是计步数据为零","answer":"<div style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">\n<div style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\" id=\"softwareDescription\" jQuery17109245358502817779=\"16\">\n<div class=\"detail_c_1 fl mt1\">\n<div style=\"POSITION: relative; PADDING-LEFT: 5%; PADDING-RIGHT: 5%\" id=\"softwareDescription\" class=\"column fl\" jQuery171049777841636180714=\"16\">\n<p class=\"ItemStep\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1.<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 7pt; font-stretch: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span>请确认小孩将手表一直是正常佩戴在手上，非佩戴状态下手表不会计步。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><?xml:namespace prefix = o /><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"ItemStep\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2.<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 7pt; font-stretch: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span>请先确认用户手表版本号，如果是不是最新版本，请用户及时升级；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"ItemStep\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3.<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 7pt; font-stretch: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span>如果已经是最新版本，确认用户能否收到摘表提醒，如果收不到摘表提醒，请用户等待下个版本解决。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">【<b>注意事项</b>】<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"ItemStep\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1.<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 7pt; font-stretch: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span>根据计步统计周期 ，运动计步数据至少需要<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>分钟才会上报，而在室内时，受网络情况和定位情况影响，最长<span lang=\"EN-US\">45</span>分钟才上报。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"ItemStep\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2.<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 7pt; font-stretch: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span>由于小孩的行走姿势比较多，我们的算法无法覆盖到所有场景，有一定的误差。例如有规律的，且持续时间比较长的晃动手臂或身体，加速度传感器数据和走路类似，小<span lang=\"EN-US\">K</span>可能会误认为你在走路，出现记步数据的偏差。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"ItemStep\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3.<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 7pt; font-stretch: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span>小<span lang=\"EN-US\">k</span>采用是间歇性的运作的算法，即隔一段时间（<span lang=\"EN-US\">2-5</span>分钟，步行<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>分钟，乘车<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>分钟，上学、放学时间<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>分钟）定位一次，定位会受到环境干扰，可能在一些无信号的地方无法定位，所以轨迹无法跟道路完全吻合，无法保证<span lang=\"EN-US\">100%</span>与实际路线一致。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n</div>\n<!--\n<div id=\"floatDiv\"></div>\n--></div>\n</div>\n</div>","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5468","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1447749735000,"seriesProductName":"K1-G01","visitedTimes":44,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"k1-g01,荣耀小k,儿童手表,k1,计步不准,计步,计步丢失,运动计步,运动数据,数据丢失,数据没有,数据为空,数据为零,数据为0,没有数据,数据不上报,数据不同步,不同步","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}